<arggraph id="micro_c183" topic_id="sports_as_family_activity" stance="pro">
  <edu id="e1"><![CDATA[Spending time together as a family engaged in sports together is a good thing.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e2"><![CDATA[It increases a sense of family togetherness,]]></edu>
  <edu id="e3"><![CDATA[gets people outside and into the fresh air and sunshine,]]></edu>
  <edu id="e4"><![CDATA[and gets the heart rate going.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e5"><![CDATA[This in turn helps to keep weight at a healthy level, and increases longevity.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e6"><![CDATA[One might argue that it's dangerous for some people to engage in strenuous activity.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e7"><![CDATA[However, many sports can be ""toned down"" for novices or those who are just starting out,]]></edu>
  <edu id="e8"><![CDATA[and with the permission of your doctor, sports are always a good thing.]]></edu>
